```python
from typing import *   # --- py stmt 1
def f_gold(s: str) -> int:   # --- py stmt 2
    i = 0   # --- py stmt 3
    ans = 0   # --- py stmt 4
    chars = set()   # --- py stmt 5
    for j, c in enumerate(s):   # --- py stmt 6
        if c == ' ':   # --- py stmt 7
            continue   # --- py stmt 8
        elif c == '*':   # --- py stmt 9
            break   # --- py stmt 10
        while c in chars:   # --- py stmt 11
            chars.remove(s[i])   # --- py stmt 12
            i += 1   # --- py stmt 13
        chars.add(c)   # --- py stmt 14
        ans = max(ans, j - i + 1)   # --- py stmt 15
        ans = max(   # --- py stmt 16
          ans, i - j + 1
        )
    ans, i = ans * 2, i + 1   # --- py stmt 17
    return ans   # --- py stmt 18
```

```python
def f_gold(nums: List[int]) -> bool:   # --- py stmt 2
    n = len(nums)   # --- py stmt 3
    s = [0] * (n + 1)   # --- py stmt 4
    for i, v in enumerate(nums):   # --- py stmt 5
        s[i + 1] = s[i] + v   # --- py stmt 6
    for j in range(3, n - 3):   # --- py stmt 7
        seen = set()   # --- py stmt 8
        for i in range(1, j - 1):   # --- py stmt 9
            if s[i] == s[j] - s[i + 1]:   # --- py stmt 10
                seen.add(s[i])   # --- py stmt 11
        for k in range(j + 2, n - 1):   # --- py stmt 12
            if s[n] - s[k + 1] == s[k] - s[j + 1] and s[n] - s[k + 1] in seen:   # --- py stmt 13
                return True   # --- py stmt 14
    return False   # --- py stmt 15
```

```javascript
function findSubarrayWithEqualSum(nums) {   // --- py stmt 2
    let length = nums.length;   // --- py stmt 3
    let prefixSum = new Array(length + 1).fill(0);   // --- py stmt 4
    for (let i = 0; i < nums.length; i++) {   // --- py stmt 5
        prefixSum[i + 1] = prefixSum[i] + nums[i];   // --- py stmt 6
    }
    for (let j = 3; j < length - 3; j++) {   // --- py stmt 7
        let seenPrefixSums = new Set();   // --- py stmt 8
        for (let i = 1; i < j - 1; i++) {   // --- py stmt 9
            if (prefixSum[i] == prefixSum[j] - prefixSum[i + 1]) {   // --- py stmt 10
                seenPrefixSums.add(prefixSum[i]);   // --- py stmt 11

        }
        for (let k = j + 2; k < length - 1; k++) {   // --- py stmt 12
```
